About Us
/$
$
Stop in for fabulous food & service at lunch or dinner.  We have a great selection of appetizers, a full bar and delicious homemade desserts.  Our lunch menu offers freshly made soup, sandwiches, burgers, entree salads and baskets.  Our dinner menu features casual meals like burgers and flatbreads and coursed meals like prime rib, filet mignon, pork chops, chicken dishes and broiled salmon - all with salad and side dishes.  We have two dining areas; our recently renovated dining room and the Cock & Bull Pub area.  All food items are available for dine-in, take-out and delivery.  We accept reservations for dinner and walk-ins are always welcome.  Ownership is very active in operations and a great roster of management and staff is always on duty.  We have on-site parking and guest Wi-Fi.  We have a private party room for special events and meetings.  This room can be reserved by advance arrangement.  Your complete enjoyment is our mission.  We look forward to seeing you soon!
